t HTTP check on the Web Server's public IP (e.g., Port 80/443).Uptime Assurance: Confirms the deployment was successful and the website is accessible to the public.NagiosHealth Check: Runs a PING check to ensure the server is online and reachable.Infrastructure Assurance: Confirms the underlying network and server OS are stable.